      • onEvent

        boolean onEvent(T event,
                boolean isEndOfBatch)
         throws Exception
        Called on receipt of an event.
        Parameters:
        event - The event.
        isEndOfBatch - True if this is the last event in the current batch, false otherwise.
        Returns:
        True to continue processing the current batch, false to halt the current batch.

        Exception - On error processing the event.
